snippet.title: The Bullpen: Inflation From Build Back Better
snippet.description:
Amber Athey, Washington editor for The Spectator, enters The Bullpen to discuss Joe Manchin and Biden's Build Back Better plan. Tell us what you think in the comments below. 

Hosts: Dr. Rashad Richey, Amber Athey

Cast: Dr. Rashad Richey, Amber Athey

***
